{
  "stem": "19055.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know if with any interest if I describe her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She had a, an extremely high education.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She spoke many languages-- French, English, German, Czech, Slovak, Hungaian-- unfortunately, never learned any Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Later on, when I learned myself, I remember this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is-- I'm filling in a gap in my mother's education.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she played piano very good, classical piano.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Extremely energetic woman-- she played tennis and swam.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she belonged actually to a, a club, a gentry club where Jews were not very welcome in, in my little town.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was the only place they had a tennis court where I picked balls for, for them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But she was welcome, because she was a good tennis player.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Her social life was extremely intense.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She organized evenings and dinners, where they were literally evenings where they would read poems.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she played bridge sometimes in the late night when I was mad because I, I couldn't sleep as a little child.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were fighting in the other room on the bridge game.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I would say especially in those times, for a woman she, she could have said a Renaissance woman.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They were a very loving couple.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as I said, I, I really never recall any fights.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm very fortunate to say that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my childhood was peaceful and home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and I brought these memories to my own family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you said that your father had been brought up in an Orthodox family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father yielded in that respect, I assume.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He, he did not demand a, a kosher home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother was willing to, to run the house in a traditional way otherwise.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As I mentioned, the, the holidays were kept.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
